0464b\" sizes=\"(max-width: 479px) 96vw, (max-width: 767px) 90vw, (max-width: 991px) 87vw, 100vw\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/5fa25a5a5bb441b26f7b8557/5fc4bf57234e05469c144e59_Car-with-Icons-p-1080.jpeg 1080w, https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/5fa25a5a5bb441b26f7b8557/5fc4bf57234e05469c144e59_Car-with-Icons.jpg 1510w\" class=\"image-6\"><div id=\"w-node-_89ed838e-c95a-f2a6-d8be-89781d0e2be1-1bf0464b\" class=\"column-01\"><h2 class=\"h2\">Battery &amp; Tires </h2><p class=\"paragraph-5\">If the battery is older than one year or defective in anyway it will be replaced and we’ll also fit a new set of tires for you so that you shouldn’t have to spend any money on your new ride </p></div><div id=\"w-node-b25b7613-d515-e122-b154-ba3647c301c2-1bf0464b\" class=\"column-01\"><h2 class=\"h2\">Accident Free!</h2><p class=\"paragraph-5\">What if this car as been in an accident? At NL Cars we made the decision to stay away from cars that have been in accidents. We also don’t buy cars that have been resprayed. We want your new ride to feel like a new car to you so we will also remove all minor dents and scratches. &nbsp;</p></div><div id=\"w-node-_62f95927-bfae-492f-51ba-23d0b2870c2d-1bf0464b\" class=\"column-01\"><h2 class=\"h2\">Service</h2><p class=\"paragraph-5\">Each car goes through a rigorous bumper to bumper check. Before you take delivery your new ride will receive a full service including but not limited to air filter, oil filter, fuel filter and oil change &nbsp;the brakes and suspension will be checked. </p></div></div><div class=\"section-22\"><h1 class=\"h2 center\">did you know?</h1><div data-delay=\"2000\" data-animation=\"slide\" class=\"slider-8 w-slider\" data-autoplay=\"true\" data-easing=\"ease\" data-hide-arrows=\"false\" data-disable-swipe=\"false\" data-autoplay-limit=\"0\" data-nav-spacing=\"3\" data-duration=\"500\" data-infinite=\"true\" role=\"region\" aria-label=\"carousel\"><div class=\"mask-2 w-slider-mask\" id=\"w-slider-