413_121672986_1825447200929244_5228691080501757520_o-p-500.jpeg 500w, https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/5fa25a5a5bb441b26f7b8557/5fbf9289c755c6239b0b1413_121672986_1825447200929244_5228691080501757520_o-p-1080.jpeg 1080w, https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/5fa25a5a5bb441b26f7b8557/5fbf9289c755c6239b0b1413_121672986_1825447200929244_5228691080501757520_o.jpg 1440w\" alt=\"\" class=\"image-fill\"></div><a id=\"w-node-df53c5ba-0706-1a07-3b91-0db6078ba2b8-1bf0464b\" href=\"/cars\" class=\"button w-button\">ALL CARS</a></div><div class=\"the-difference\"><div id=\"w-node-_78d8ef2b-7dc7-06a2-9753-2b35150cf421-1bf0464b\" class=\"div-block-41\"><div class=\"rich-text-block-7 w-richtext\"><h2>What Makes Us Different?</h2><p>Buy choosing to shop for a used car you can save a LOT of money! For example, a 3 month old Volkswagen Polo with only 10 000km on the clock is on average 25% cheaper than a new one. That means if that if a new Polo costs R330 000 on the floor you be could be driving a basically new one for around R250 000 As the models get older there prices drop drastically you could buy BMW’s flagship model 2 years down the line at less than half the price it came out at. </p><p>The catch 22 is that when buying used you can take on risk. This is where NL cars steps in to create a win win situation for you and reduce your risk! We authentically care about our customers and place high value in our reputation and name. <strong><em>Put shortly we don’t sell skoro skoro’s!</em></strong> We pay extra attention to detail and we believe in doing things right! Each car that comes in goes through a thorough inspection and before you take delivery will have a full service and be fitted with new tires and a new battery. </p><p>We understand that you may value the car that you are buying from us the same as a billionaire might value a new Lamborghini and we endeavor to give you the closest to new used car experience that you can find and we promise to treat you like you are buying a new car, whether you are shopping for a Toyota corolla or a Bentley because we are for everyone!</p></div></div><img src=\"https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/5fa25a5a5bb441b26f7b8557/5fa25c34e8121d4619d5c2e7_mmm3-01.png\" loading=\"lazy\" id=\"w-node-_78d8ef2b-7dc7-06a2-9753-2b35150cf42d-1bf0464b\" sizes=\"(max-width: 991px) 100vw, 25vw\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/5fa25a5a5bb441b26f7b8557/5fa25c34e8121d4619d5c2e7_mmm3-01-p-500.png 500w, https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/5fa25a5a5bb441b26f7b8557/5fa25c34e8121d4619d5c2e7_mmm3-01.png 640w\" class=\"image-8\"><div class=\"div-block-51 tablet\"><div class=\"rich-text-block-8 w-richtext\"><h2>Contact Us</h2><p>23 Ayliff Street. Newcastle<br>Kwazulu Natal, South Africa<br>C: 078 321 2027<br>E: nicolas@nlcars.co.za</p></div><a href=\"/contact\" class=\"button-6 w-button\">Go to Page</a></div><img src=\"https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/5fa25a5a5bb441b26f7b8557/5fa25c40c9185355f007eda1_IMG_0221.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" id=\"w-node-_78d8ef2b-7dc7-06a2-9753-2b35150cf42e-1bf0464b\" sizes=\"(max-width: 991px) 100vw, 25vw\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/5fa25a5a5bb441b26f7b8557/5fa25c40c9185355f007eda1_IMG_0221-p-1080.jpeg 1080w, https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/5fa25a5a5bb441b26f7b8557/5fa25c40c9185355f007eda1_IMG_0221-p-1600.jpeg 1600w, https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/5fa25a5a5bb441b26f7b8557/5fa25c40c9185355f007eda1_IMG_0221-p-2000.jpeg 2000w, https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/5fa25a5a5bb441b26f7b8557/5fa25c40c9185355f007eda1_IMG_0221-p-2600.jpeg 2600w, https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/5fa25a5a5bb441b26f7b8557/5fa25c40c9185355f007eda1_IMG_0221.jpg 3155w\" class=\"image-9\"><div id=\"w-node-_78d8ef2b-7dc7-06a2-9753-2b35150cf42f-1bf0464b\" class=\"div-block-48\"><div class=\"rich-text-block-6 w-richtext\"><h2>ABOUT OUR TEAM</h2><p>NL Cars is the used car dealership for everyone. Founded in March 2017 we have grown from strength to strength because we are guided by a str